name: Hawa Cat Halloween Nightmare
description: Hawa Cat really gets afraid at Halloween. Sometimes she stays up all night making the sign of the cross to make sure no vampires or goblins get to her. This 2021  Halloween  she got dressed and went to the mirror to put in her eyeliner, and SCREAM!!!!!! Her flesh was gone and she was a skeleton and her home was turned into a haunted house.
